sentences.text: A'indeccu mane jipa mani canse'fa'chone condase'cho, tsendeccuta tsu Carivene ccuyapa ji'fachondeccu (tsendeccuta tsu boña etnolinguistico Chibcha'su'fa).
Tsendeccuta tsu Caribene chiga sombo'jefanga ji'fa'chondeccu, tsa'caen jipa tsu aindeccu jacan'cho andenga nampi'fa.
Tsa sardina na'enga toya'caen Payamino na'en enttingefanga toya'caen tsu nampi'fa nortefanga japa Apichaccu naipe.
Vama tevaensundeccu suqquia'caen tsa'caen tsaimbi'tsse jacamba tsu tise'pa jacan'choma nani'fa.
Tsa tsu suye in'jan biase'fa tsu 10. 000 canqquefave.
Tsa'cansi tsu va condase'pama atesu'fa'choja su, tsave tayopiyi tsu a'indeccuja canse'fa'cho.
Tevaensundeccuta tsu incandeccune'qque condase'fa.
(Huayna Capac) ccottaccone Chapini andepa tsu aindeccu Hatunique tsa cofan na'eni canse'fa'choma atte'fa; faesu tevaensundeccuta tsu iyi'cco'aqque toya an'mbian'fa.
Tsa'caeñi gi re'ri'ccoe atesu'cho'fa ña'me bia'a tsu toya Colon jimbiteja aindeccu tsampini, tsambi'ta ccottacconi cansesundeccune.
Tsa'caen tson'chota tsu jongaesuma chavaeñe ñotsse jacan'fa'cho iyiccoya'chove jacan'fambi tsu, tsomba aindeccuta tsu tson'fa mingae jacamba chavaeña'chove'qque.
Tsa'caen tsu ashaen'fa tsa Pimamampirone.

Tsa quinerondeccu toya'caen caucherondeccu: Quinome ttatta'su, toya'caen cauchove ttattasundeccu tsu jacan'fa a'indeccu tsambi'ta suye osefa'paveja tsa siglo XIX siglo XXma otie, ña'me injengembichoa manda'choi'ccu semaemba vanaeñe.
